data.title: Offline Search
data.text:
Off-Line Search Service

We have the vast majority of our total inventory cataloged and online. If you were unable to find the book you wanted, then please complete the form below and we will search our off-line inventory for you. If we don't have the book in our inventory we can enter it as a request and when it comes in we'll give you a call or drop you an e-mail. If you want us to keep looking, please include a note to add it to your "Request" list..

We have been very successful in finding books for our customers. We are experts in the book business; let us complete your book search for you.

Please complete as much of the form as possible, or email us at [email protected], or call us at 563-355-2310. The more detail you provide, the more likely we will find the exact book you want.
